<p>ë°©ì•ˆ1. Installation via a sidecar container <a href="https://argo-cd.readthedocs.io/en/stable/user-guide/config-management-plugins/#installing-a-cmp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">(new, starting with Argo CD v2.4.0)<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></p>
